room_title: Escape room "Strange Brew" by Pikes Peak Escape Rooms in Colorado Springs
room_address: 1826 E Platte Ave Suite 200 Colorado Springs, CO 80909
room_description:
Tonight is a special night that comes along once in a millennia. Sisters Eleanor and Beatrice have been preparing for most of their lives. They will cast the spell of spells to dissolve the wall between what is natural and what is not. YOU must stop them. If you fail, things really go bump in the night.

Will YOU save the world on time?
